title: Best Bits of the Week Show with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Honeymoon Drama (Week of 1/4)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week Show with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Honeymoon Drama (Week of 1/4)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings on Raymundo to talk about what we didn't get to hear from his honeymoon. Eddie gives some more details about his foster kids and Lunchbox talks about his latest prank call.
